======================================================================

KonnectionMonitor

This is a little utility I wrote a few years ago to monitor current
open connections on linux, aiming to mimic tcpview for windows. It
uses the proc filesystem as I found it in kernel 2.6.22 (afair).
There might be better ways to do this by now.

Home: http://kde-apps.org/content/show.php?content=140883

